{"tid":2187341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人老豆老母成日嘈交？","createTime":"2020-09-03T14:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T14:59:12.000Z","uid":253763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0b145b3f5065c81c97ddcabc9136686cc363b8c7","tid":2187341,"uid":253763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"真係好撚煩，幾廿歲人仲為啲濕鳩無謂野嘈。老豆動不動就玩離家出走，老母就以為自己仲細要人好似公主咁氹。間屋本身已經細，我又無自己一間房，避都無得避，嘈到我好撚死。<br />\n屌咁撚憎大家就離婚啦，日日為埋啲on9野嘈。"},{"pid":"42e1775a9b8d9635efd8a7a91f82c3a19c4289e4","tid":2187341,"uid":187201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:28:52.000Z","msg":"到有能力就搬出去，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3fb44ac33397a7d12195f6deaa67eb07f985f0","tid":2187341,"uid":253763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42e1775a9b8d9635efd8a7a91f82c3a19c4289e4","tid":2187341,"uid":187201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:28:52.000Z","msg":"到有能力就搬出去，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"成間屋都係戾氣。我細個係一個好開心嘅人，自從六、七年前佢地開始嗌交之後，我一聽到嗌交聲就好想死，情緒長年崩緊，心理輔導都見埋。<br />\n就算出街同frd玩到幾開心都好，一返到屋企望住個戾氣屋企就好撚想死。"},{"pid":"2e0894b171e16b525256b1db926caae0dfa44ff4","tid":2187341,"uid":21575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"睇到以為係一年前嘅自己開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申頂唔順已搬"},{"pid":"e8f5c6b1163b911652e3ef944334238d4224362d","tid":2187341,"uid":253763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e0894b171e16b525256b1db926caae0dfa44ff4","tid":2187341,"uid":21575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"睇到以為係一年前嘅自己開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申頂唔順已搬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"我諗住下年開始返工就搬 真係好撚辛苦"},{"pid":"b480e3561e2bf61e37ffd65826b